715690f-a.title: Manhattan: 157th Street (West) - Amsterdam Avenue
715690f-a.text:
502 West 157th Street, adjoining the S.W. corner of Amsterdam Ave.
Building shown is the synagogue of the Cong. Ahavath Israel.
October 12, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
